---
// AboutSection — Short paragraph about the business background, approach, and Cambridgeshire locality
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about__inner">
    <h2 class="about__heading">About Warboys Gutter Clearing</h2>
    <p class="about__text">
      We're a friendly, family-run business with years of experience serving Warboys and the surrounding areas. We take pride in offering a reliable, professional service with a personal touch — no fuss, no mess, just the job done properly.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
  }

  .about__inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about__heading {
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about__text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }
</style>
